title: Barbie - Barbie (1985)  Alexander Bard as disco dragqueen Barbie
description:
The self-titled album by disco drag queen Barbie (Alexander Bard) released 1985. 

Together with the dancers Katanga (Camilla Henemark) and Farouk (Jean-Pierre Barda) Bard formed the group Army of Lovers. Their rare debut single is included as bonus tracks here.

Ripped from vinyl. Never released on CD.

01. Passion of the groove
02. Bam bam boom
03. The locomotion
04. The girl from Ipanema
05. Sex is the dynamite drug
06. Prostitution twist
07. Hot stuff
08. Rock it up
09. Yes sir i can boogie
10. Johnny Johnny (duet with Cia Berg)

Bonus tracks:
11. When the night is cold (Army of lovers)
12. Shoot that laserbeam (Army of lovers)
